Ricky Kelman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ricky_Kelman 0 Rickey William Kelman (born July 6, 1950), is a former child and young adult actor who appeared in film and on television from 1954 to 1974. He had supporting roles in two single-season situation comedies, The Dennis O'Keefe Show (1959-1960) on CBS and Our Man Higgins (1962-1963) on ABC.
